{"tid":301872,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚心啦屌你老母廢老 讓你都要屌鳩人","createTime":"2017-06-29T03:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T06:57:19.000Z","uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc0a0854b8912fe690179e9a025e486fd3db954","tid":301872,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:18:42.000Z","msg":"真係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說啱啱我喺彌敦道截的士<br />\n咁我喺個上落客個位度等啦<br />\n等左陣就有個阿伯插撚左入嚟<br />\n仲有個工人同個坐喺輪椅嘅阿婆<br />\n佢阿伯望到我就特撚登企前十米截<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好都算</span></span><br />\n有架吉嘅的士嚟咗<br />\n駛左去牌果邊 (啫係我個位)<br />\n咁我都諗住話見人地有個行動唔方便嘅阿婆樣比佢地先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就諗住開門同個司機講聲<br />\n個廢老見到勁撚大聲話：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「喂咪撚上呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span></span><br />\n我嘅反應係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後跑鳩過嚟話知唔知乜撚係禮貌 <br />\n又話見到有老人家都唔撚讓 死𡃁妹冇家教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我粒聲都冇出佢地就上車走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母啦 係撚要衝出嚟鳩 做好心又要比你咁撚樣屌 好彩我唔撚係趕時間啫 真係好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60777915b55065c1ab72987a070b5dc3360ce9cd","tid":301872,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌"},{"pid":"e13f4367903398d1135c5437f460b421f8b8ef96","tid":301872,"uid":95520,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"你仲比佢上你都夠on9啦<br />\n廢老唔即場屌有咩用?<br />\n放上連登佢地會睇到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5a03b6dc61c875a9ad69c46437adceb5c5b41f","tid":301872,"uid":114541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:21:53.000Z","msg":"如果我係你，照上唔理佢，讓比佢係人情，唔讓比佢係道理。"},{"pid":"e0ea697a7e63dbadf1f5191e43575b4698914c29","tid":301872,"uid":3066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:22:58.000Z","msg":"弱智 上車啦 <br />\n做女人做到你咁<br />\n淨係識上網屌"},{"pid":"ae6f1484c9250919ff480885332777443bee2de3","tid":301872,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"俾我會照鬧佢地，老又點？大晒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbcdcb2e9f476bb5c5c856299c7e8cec2db3924","tid":301872,"uid":124942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:25:44.000Z","msg":"即係咁，柒就柒在你又要扮好人，比狗屌又要唔識還拖咁囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你都廢閪事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5995e3680247584d87232ed07bf96984a6b53acb","tid":301872,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係咁，柒就柒在你又要扮好人，比狗屌又要唔識還拖咁囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你都廢閪事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最柒就係放上黎比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0731aceea3518b8adee9d96447c3dffc00228c","tid":301872,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果我係你，照上唔理佢，讓比佢係人情，唔讓比佢係道理。</blockquote><br />\n人乜撚野情 係搶奪 係強盜"},{"pid":"13d0015c3b86b7411723b587d0eb50b78edbee51","tid":301872,"uid":21837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"其實你真係讓嘅話會唔會同司機講呀<br />\n我覺得好奇怪姐<br />\n<br />\n你會點講？<br />\n司機，我讓俾呀婆上先<br />\n咁樣？<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣做好人都好嘔心喎<br />\n好似做好事要人知咁先去做<br />\n<br />\n你有心讓應該係同個老人家講你上先啦<br />\n而唔係同司機講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf328f909fceb30152ab0f4eed187dbd63057dfe","tid":301872,"uid":2857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bb78e8ec05ecd34a1208c51b391a52b451c0b2","tid":301872,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"你係要讓洗撚開門同司機講<br />\n用手勢/指一指唔得？<br />\n比人誤會被屌又走上黎博同情發泄<br />\n<br />\n其實結論係 你根本就係弱智"},{"pid":"ebb859eb82bb35562929aba40e1e49952301a6ec","tid":301872,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:52:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係咁，柒就柒在你又要扮好人，比狗屌又要唔識還拖咁囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你都廢閪事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家諗番都覺自己太好人 但見到人地有個行動唔方便嘅呀婆 即刻收撚左火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6d4c77269503ebb04d43d23bffceafea028dba","tid":301872,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係見有個呀婆先唔撚同佢嘈 如果唔係一定搞撚大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60294ff655fb9038f34ff14daef195ada8cd4c09","tid":301872,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係見有個呀婆先唔撚同佢嘈 如果唔係一定搞撚大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係廢"},{"pid":"f58a65b33ad3a1b669ce0f6210dc3aca975ac5d5","tid":301872,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你真係讓嘅話會唔會同司機講呀<br />\n我覺得好奇怪姐<br />\n<br />\n你會點講？<br />\n司機，我讓俾呀婆上先<br />\n咁樣？<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣做好人都好嘔心喎<br />\n好似做好事要人知咁先去做<br />\n<br />\n你有心讓應該係同個老人家講你上先啦<br />\n而唔係同司機講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面咪講左佢地企前好多諗住快過我截 所以咪講聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73a0b7d64659c998e876da4465c5085a54c2197","tid":301872,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係見有個呀婆先唔撚同佢嘈 如果唔係一定搞撚大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係廢</blockquote><br />\n都可以話係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"h